w out of fashion. Among numerous well-known and influential bearers are the British novelists  Jean Plaidy  (  Eleanor Hibbert ,  1910–93 ) and  Jean Rhys  (  Ella Gwendolen Rees Williams ,  1894–1979 ), British actress  Jean Simmons  (  1929–2010 ), and American-born actress  Jean Seberg  (  1938–79 ). It is also found as a variant spelling of the masculine name   Gene ."],"variants":[{"name":"John","meanings":["form of   John  , also used quite frequently in the English-speaking world. In Northern Ireland it is sometimes found as a variant of   Ewan ."]},{"name":"Jeane","meanings":["Variant spelling of   Jean ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Jean was born about 1525, in Midlothian, Scotland. She married William Phelps. They were the parents of at least 2 daughters. She died before 1625, in Midlothian, Scotland, United Kingdom."},"et":{"Abt. 1525–Bef. 1625":"umbes 1525–enne 1625","1522–1620":"1522–1620","1541–1600":"1541–1600","1542–1600":"1542–1600","1525–1625":"1525–1625","1525":"1525","1600":"1600","before 1620":"enne 1620","Bef. 1625":"enne 1625","Abt. 1525":"umbes 1525","1522":"1522","1620":"1620","1542":"1542","Bef. 1600":"enne 1600","1541":"1541","about 1541":"umbes 1541","1625":"1625"," Midlothian Scotland":"Midlothian, Šotimaa, United Kingdom","Midlothian, Scotland":"Midlothian, Šotimaa, United Kingdom","Scotland":"Šotimaa, United Kingdom","Middleton, Midlothian, Scotland":"Middleton, Midlothian, Šotimaa, United Kingdom","Dunlop, Ayrshire, Scotland":"Dunlop, Ayrshire, Scotland"},"fi":{"Abt. 1525–Bef. 1625":"noin 1525–ennen vuotta 1625","1522–1620":"1522–1620","1541–1600":"1541–1600","1542–1600":"1542–1600","1525–1625":"1525–1625","1525":"1525","1600":"1600","before 1620":"ennen vuotta 1620","Bef. 1625":"ennen vuotta 1625","Abt. 1525":"noin 1525","1522":"1522","1620":"1620","1542":"1542","Bef. 1600":"ennen vuotta 1600","1541":"1541","about 1541":"noin 1541","1625":"1625"," Midlothian Scotland":"Midlothian, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Midlothian, Scotland":"